      "title": "Installation And Commissioning",
      "description": "Precision Machine Tools Service Team has successfully completed the installation & commissioning more than 50 machines in the United Arabic Emirates  and Middle East region. Precision Machine Tools has experienced and trained service engineers capable of installing wide variety of CNC Machines with Fanuc/Siemens/Heidenheim CNC control systems. Installation and commissioning must follow Scientific and Professional way of assembling machine using proper tools, levelling of the machine. Switching on with necessary care and demonstrating the’ machine accuracy as guaranteed. Proper installation ensures the machine’s best Performance, Reliability and Ease of is maintenance. Customers can use PRECISION MACHINE TOOLS LLC team which has Trained and Experienced Service engineers with the necessary Tools and Calibration equipment required for I & C.",
