    {
      "title": "Breakdown Services",
      "description": "A machine’s breakdown true cost is difficult to measure. Machine breakdown at a critical time can not only cost huge business losses but also business relationship between companies.  The biggest relief at such a critical time comes from quickly putting the machine into operation. Precision Machine Tools LLC understands the importance of machine uptime for any industry and offers quick response for any emergency breakdown service requests and ensures that machine is put back into operation in the shortest possible period.",
