    },
    {
      "title": "Annual Maintenance Contract (AMC)",
      "description": "Machine maintenance can be done periodically (Periodic Preventive Maintenance) or when failure occurs (Breakdown Maintenance). Most companies focus on reactive maintenance which is maintenance after failure occurs.  Periodic maintenance is a form of Proactive maintenance done at fixed intervals of time, which helps in minimizing machine downtime and production loss. Annual maintenance contract (AMC) between customer and Precision Machine Tools ensures the machines maintenance activity carried out at agreed intervals of time and in a specified way to minimize machine failure and consequent machine downtime and production loss. Precision Machine Tools has a team of qualified and experienced service engineers stationed in UAE for providing AMC Services at a reasonable cost and time schedules.",
      "icon": "Settings",
      "details": "CNC,VMC,HMC,VTL,CONVENTIONAL MACHINES, GRINDING MACHINES, ALL INDUSTRIAL CNC MACHINES",
      "imageUrl": "/uploads/services/1781865630448-image_ea5b1c23.png",
      "id": 1781865646583,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-19T10:40:46.583Z",
      "updatedAt": "2026-06-19T10:41:33.763Z"
    },
    {
      "title": "Retrofitting of CNC Machine",
      "description": "CNC machines used in heavy engineering Industries generally fail due to aging electronics. Due to the Huge cost and Larger lead times, it is not cost effective to replace these machines. Retrofitting such machines with latest CNC control, servo and spindle motors, drives, electrical components while retaining the mechanical components, is an excellent option for restoring their accuracy, uptime, and productivity. This not only results in huge savings by avoiding purchase of New expensive machines but also saves time as retrofitting can be done in much less time than manufacturing a new machine. Precision Machine Tools LLC have nearly 10 years of experience in retrofitting of such large machines such as VMC, HMC, Boring machines with Fanuc/Siemens/Heidenheim CNC Controllers to the Benifit of many Satisfied customers. Euro gulf has a team of Highly Qualified Engineers in UAE and India to support customer in every step of retrofit from CNC selection, electrical schematic design, panel rewiring, machine rewiring, electromechanical support, application programming and after sale service.",
      "icon": "Settings",
      "details": "CNC,VMC,VTL,CONVENTIONAL MACHINES, GRINDING MACHINES",
