      "title": "Spare Parts and Accessories",
      "description": "No matter how well CNC machines are designed and built, over time certain components will eventually wear out and fail. Similarly, no matter how well operators are trained, accidents occur due to some unexpected human errors. During the machine breakdowns, effective sourcing, supply of quality spare parts is very critical to quickly put back the machine in to operation. Precision Machine Tools LLC with their vast experience in maintenance and repair services have through knowledge of machine parts availability and can arrange for any critical spare part within reasonable time.",
      "icon": "Settings",
      "details": "CNC,VMC,HMC,VTL,CONVENTIONAL MACHINES, GRINDING MACHINES, ALL INDUSTRIAL CNC MACHINES",
