    },
    {
      "title": "Machine Relocation",
      "description": "Expensive CNC machines are an important asset of any company. It is therefore very important to keep them in operation all the time with least downtime. In the eventuality of their relocation from one shop to another or one Factory site to another site, it should be done with utmost care so as not to damage any part and in least possible time so as not to cause any production loss. \nIt should therefore be entrusted to professionals who are experienced and have right tools and knowledge to execute the job. Finding the correct relocation services team is key for hassle free and safe relocation of complex and expensive machines. After relocation the machines static and dynamic accuracies must once again be verified for accuracy as per relevant standards before taking machines into production. Precision Machine Tools LLC team’s Professional approach, meticulous planning and experience guarantee worry-free machine relocation and calibration before handing over machine for production.",
